page.title: 16STEPHEN'S THURSDAY
page.content: I live in{Ince Blundell}with my mum and dad and 2 younger brothers.I am 10 years old. I get up at 8am and have cereal and toast.After this I get washed and clean my teeth then I watch morning T.V. or something on the video.I get to school about 8.50am and play with my friends until 9am. we do maths,english and craft in the morning with a break at 10.30.I like annoying the girls at playtime. At 12 o'clock we have dinner.Sometimes I bring sandwiches. After that we play for about half an hour. In the afternoon we play netball with Little Crosby school-we havent got enough children for 2 teams.we go home at 3.30pm.I get changed,watch T.V. and have tea. I go to bed about 8.30 p.m.
